      <title>墨西哥央行对未来降息保持谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mexico-s-central-bank-strikes-wary-tone-on-any-future-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥央行成员在宣布自 2021 年以来首次降息时对国内经济和通胀的弹性表示担忧，并暗示未来的降息将是渐进的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mexico-s-central-bank-strikes-wary-tone-on-any-future-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
